T*
(1. Overview) Tj
T*
(-----------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(NexCart is a full-stack e-commerce platform with a customer-facing storefront and an admin) Tj
T*
(operations console. The project is split into a React \(Vite\) frontend and a Spring Boot) Tj
T*
(backend, backed by a MySQL database. Authentication is handled via JWT stored in an HttpOnly) Tj
T*
(cookie, and most API routes are protected by a custom authentication filter.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Repository Layout) Tj
T*
(--------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Frontend app: `nexcart`) Tj
T*
(- Backend app: `nexcartBackEnd`) Tj
T*
(- Additional dashboard template: `dashboard_import/react-admin-dashboard-master` \(separate) Tj
T*
(  React project, not wired into the main NexCart app\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Tech Stack) Tj
T*
(-------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Frontend) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- React 19 + Vite) Tj
T*
(- React Router) Tj
T*
(- Tailwind CSS \(via `@tailwindcss/vite`\) and custom CSS) Tj
T*
(- Axios and Fetch) Tj
T*
(- Recharts for analytics charts) Tj
T*
(- Framer Motion + Lottie for animations) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backend) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Spring Boot 3.4 \(Java 17\)) Tj
T*
(- Spring Web + Spring Data JPA) Tj
T*
(- MySQL database) Tj
T*
(- JWT auth \(jjwt\)) Tj
T*
(- Razorpay payment integration) Tj
T*
(- JUnit tests) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. Running Locally) Tj
T*
(------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
