T*
(- Custom filter `AuthenticationFilter` protects `/api/` and `/admin/` routes.) Tj
T*
(- Admin routes require role `ADMIN`.) Tj
T*
(- Public routes are limited to:) Tj
T*
(- `POST /api/users/register`) Tj
T*
(- `POST /api/auth/login`) Tj
T*
() Tj
