(9. Data Model Summary) Tj
T*
(---------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main entities and key fields) Tj
T*
(- User: `userId`, `username`, `email`, `password`, `role`, `status`, `blocked`, `address`,) Tj
T*
(  `createdAt`) Tj
T*
(- Product: `productId`, `name`, `description`, `price`, `stock`, `productStatus`, `category`) Tj
T*
(- Category: `categoryId`, `categoryName`, `imageUrl`) Tj
T*
(- CartItem: `user`, `product`, `quantity`) Tj
T*
(- Order: `orderId`, `userId`, `subtotal`, `shipping`, `tax`, `total`, `status`, `paymentStatus`) Tj
T*
(- OrderItem: `order`, `productId`, `quantity`, `pricePerUnit`, `totalPrice`) Tj
T*
(- Payment: `orderId`, `razorpayPaymentId`, `status`, `amount`, `userId`) Tj
T*
(- Coupon: `code`, `discountType`, `discountValue`, `expiryDate`, `usageLimit`, `active`) Tj
T*
(- Review: `productId`, `userId`, `rating`, `comment`) Tj
T*
(- SupportTicket: `ticketNumber`, `userId`, `type`, `priority`, `status`, `subject`, `message`) Tj
T*
(- ReturnRequest: `orderId`, `productId`, `userId`, `requestType`, `status`, `refundStatus`) Tj
T*
(- SystemSetting: `settingKey`, `settingValue`) Tj
