(14. Build and Deployment) Tj
T*
(------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Frontend build) Tj
T*
(- `npm run build`) Tj
T*
(- Output: `nexcart/dist`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backend build) Tj
T*
(- `./mvnw.cmd -DskipTests package`) Tj
T*
(- Output: `nexcartBackEnd/target/.jar`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deployment checklist) Tj
T*
(- Configure production database) Tj
T*
(- Set JWT secret and payment keys as environment variables) Tj
T*
(- Update allowed CORS origins) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(15. Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(-------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Common issues) Tj
T*
(- 401 Unauthorized: login cookie missing or expired.) Tj
T*
(- 403 Forbidden: user is blocked or not admin.) Tj
T*
(- CORS errors: frontend port not listed in allowed origins.) Tj
T*
(- JWT secret error: must be at least 64 bytes.) Tj
T*
(- Razorpay errors: verify keys and callback payload.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(16. Security and Operational Notes) Tj
T*
(----------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Consider enabling HTTPS and secure cookies in production.) Tj
T*
(- Move secrets out of `application.properties`.) Tj
T*
(- Enable Spring Security for production hardening.) Tj
T*
(- Add rate limiting on auth and payment endpoints.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(End of Document) Tj
